data.description: This tastefully renovated home located in the heart of Satellite Beach boasts over 2500sf of living space.  The split plan features a master bedroom with a spa-like master bath, and an additional room which could have multiple uses i.e. an exquisite walk in closet, a nursery, an office.  The other secondary bedrooms are all oversized and share the up-dated full bath complete with subway tile.  The kitchen is in the heart of the home with stainless steel appliances and granite tops, open shelving, wood ceiling.  High-end wood laminate flooring throughout home with the exception of secondary bedrooms. All doors and windows are cased. 3.5 car garage split 2 front and 1.5 side, great for additional storage or wood shop.  Close to beaches and Satellite Library and fields. A+ Schools, cul de sac
